data.description: Welcome to your PNW craftsman home over 100 years young! Her lofty main floor is sunlight filled w/ doublepane windows installed 2021 along w/ new roof, siding, ductless A/C & other updated items including plumbing & electrical. Interior flow allows 3 dogs, 3 cats & their humans to live in harmony w/ mudroom, living, dining, eat-in kitchen, bathroom, laundry on main floor & 3 bedrooms upstairs. Window placements allow breezy crossflow. Pamper your green thumb w/ blank slate level yard or keep it grassy for lack of gardening skills. Daylight basement offers extra 780 sqft insulated living space, independent alley entry, fullsize windows, tall ceiling, exposed beams and outlets every few feet! ~Comps~ NWMLS# 2129627, 2164221, 2161253
